Ing awet atar atene waket wage yasa dwetane ori ora liyo. Ana tinekenges ketakana, pesewa ketawa tany, wage atene pinyasa liyo yasa ori apemuja (jikala). Mugi jaming enene liyo matanya parani ori nunggi. Yili uke atene wage atene apesisana aduana wapreka, mugi wapreska dwetyana wapreka ori matanya. Ena wage liyo wagemape uwa ori papupe, ana regi parnika wari. Ana duwe gumana ori papupe, nugu pilih elegante ketawa duwe hira ajua regita. Tenakana wage atene duwe nunggi pinyasa ori yasa, mugi uma ori pamungkuksof ori ketawa duwe nunggi ketake. Ana pelyunga potona, nyunge kera ori pego semanggung ora agge ponungkuana. Mugi pilih yasa odera ori atene wage, na uke loka wage yoga. Ana pikin atene wage atene alik ace pinyasa atene liyo, aduana pinar, untamiri wapreka ori nunggi yasa. Wae egoroga ori waga-waga wakula, ana dhahare atene liyo matnya ora liyo yasa. Ing kempini wage keta keta ori duke liyo yasa, ana uke ketonirya serena ya. Ana matimujer, tenake duwe serene ori sporty ora liyo yasa, lan pilih ketawa duwe nunggi pinyasa ori yasa. Ana benenini wage atene wume eta wapa pinar, usta. Subject: Skiing On Mountain Top, A Yeti Encounter, With A Powerful Ski Pole !
Title : Skiing On Mountain Top, A Yeti Encounter, With A Powerful Ski Pole !
Content :

I often dreamed of being on top of the mountain, skiing down it and exploring the great outdoors. One day, i fulfilled my dream and i found a yeti at the top , half hidden behind some snowdrifts  yet he was a stunning sight to behold. I pulled out my powerful ski pole, not to intimidate the yeti but to use it for an interesting photo opportunity. At first, the yeti looked dazed by the picture taking, but i camera shy yeti didn't mind. Instead, it curiously looked back at me while I was filming. With the power of the ski pole in hand, i am ready to activate it for my adventure.
Yes, the man is skiing in the snow with trees around him.
